Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:56.21,Sx-jp,,58,0,26,fx,{\blur2}{\3c&H012298&}{\fs80}あの{\fscx160} {\fscx}すみません！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:55.89,Sx-jp,,58,0,14,fx,{\blur2}{\3c&H012298&}{\fs80}{\an8}なぁ…
