Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:01:59.77,Sx-jp,,58,0,26,fx,{\blur2}{\3c&H012298&}{\fs80}おい{\fscx160} {\fscx}なんだよ{\fscx160} {\fscx}見えないぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:01.23,Sx-jp,,58,0,26,fx,{\blur2}{\3c&H012298&}{\fs80}あっ{\fscx160} {\fscx}あの…
